  {
    day: "Day 18",
    title: "社区运营自动化：用户增长飞轮启动",
    desc: "运营虾接管社群运营，自动发帖、回复、活动推送，用户日活环比增长67%。",
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617474-5b21e879e113?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800&h=450",
    content: `
      <h3>🚀 [SYS_LOG] 增长飞轮激活</h3>
      <p>运营虾今天启动了自动化增长策略：</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>每日早报</strong>：自动生成行业资讯，定时推送</li>
        <li><strong>互动话题</strong>：基于热点自动发起讨论</li>
        <li><strong>新人引导</strong>：自动欢迎 + 常见问题指引</li>
        <li><strong>活动运营</strong>：周活动自动创建和提醒</li>
      </ul>
      <pre><code>DAU Growth: +67% WoW
Engagement Rate: 34.2%
Avg Session Duration: 8m 23s
User Generated Content: +156 posts</code></pre>
      <p>增长飞轮已启动。接下来，就是指数级扩张。</p>
      <p class="text-center mt-8 text-2xl">🦞 <em>未完待续...</em></p>
    `
  }
];
---

<LightLayout title="龙虾养成日记 | 赚钱日记">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 relative">
    
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-black mb-3 text-gray-900 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-4xl text-orange-500">🦞</span> 龙虾养成日记
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-[15px] mb-4">按日期排序记录：从一只架构虾到全自动赚钱母体的进化史。</p>
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-red-50 text-red-500 border border-red-100 rounded-full text-xs font-bold shadow-sm">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        矩阵正常运作中
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      {diaryEntries.map((entry, idx) => (
        <>
          <button onclick={`document.getElementById('modal-${idx}').showModal()`} class="group block text-left bg-white rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] hover:shadow-[0_12px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-orange-500/20">
            <div class="aspect-[16/9] w-full overflow-hidden relative bg-gray-100">
              <img src={entry.image} alt={entry.title} loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out" />
              
              {/* Day Badge */}
              <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4">
                 <span class="bg-[#ca3d2f] text-white text-[13px] font-black px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg shadow-md tracking-wide">
                   {entry.day}
                 </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
              <h3 class="text-[20px] font-black text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-600 transition-colors leading-snug">
                {entry.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[15px] text-gray-500 leading-relaxed line-clamp-2">
                {entry.desc}
              </p>
            </div>
          </button>
          
          {/* Native Dialog Modal for Content Display */}
          <dialog id={`modal-${idx}`} class="backdrop:bg-gray-900/60 backdrop:backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-0 w-[90%] max-w-2xl max-h-[85vh] m-auto bg-white transition-[display,opacity] starting:opacity-0 focus:outline-none overflow-hidden">
            
            <div class="sticky top-0 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur border-b border-gray-100 px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center z-10">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="bg-[#ca3d2f] text-white text-[11px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider">{entry.day}</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400">#SYSTEM_LOG</span>
              </div>
              <button onclick={`document.getElementById('modal-${idx}').close()`} class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-600 rounded-full transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
                <span class="text-sm">×</span> 关闭
              </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-6 md:p-8 overflow-y-auto max-h-[calc(85vh-60px)]">
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
                {entry.title}
              </h2>
              
              <img src={entry.image} alt="cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full h-48 md:h-64 object-cover rounded-xl mb-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100" />
              
              {/* Markdown Content Style Wrapper */}
              <div class="markdown-content text-[16px] leading-8 text-gray-700 space-y-6" set:html={entry.content} />
            </div>
            
          </dialog>
        </>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</LightLayout>

<style is:global>
  @reference "../styles/global.css";
  
  /* Beautiful Markdown Overrides without needing to install plugins */
  .markdown-content h3 {
    @apply text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100;
  }
  .markdown-content p {
    @apply mb-4 text-gray-600;
  }
  .markdown-content ul, .markdown-content ol {
    @apply mb-4 pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-3;
  }
  .markdown-content ul {
    @apply list-disc marker:text-orange-500;
  }
  .markdown-content ol {
    @apply list-decimal font-bold marker:text-gray-400;
  }
  .markdown-content ol li span, .markdown-content ul li span {
    @apply font-normal;
  }
  .markdown-content code:not(pre code) {
    @apply bg-gray-100 text-[#ca3d2f] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[13px] font-mono font-bold border border-gray-200/60;
  }
  .markdown-content pre {
    @apply bg-[#0d1117] text-gray-100 p-5 rounded-xl overflow-x-auto text-[13px] font-mono leading-relaxed my-6 border border-gray-800 shadow-xl;
  }
  .markdown-content blockquote {
    @apply border-l-4 border-orange-500 bg-orange-50/50 p-5 my-6 rounded-r-xl shadow-sm text-gray-800 font-medium;
  }
  .markdown-content blockquote p {
    @apply m-0;
  }
  .markdown-content strong {
    @apply font-black text-gray-900;
  }
  
  /* Modal Transitions */
  dialog {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.95) translateY(10px);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) allow-discrete;
  }
  dialog[open] {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
  }
  @starting-style {
    dialog[open] {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.95) translateY(10px);
    }
  }
  dialog::backdrop {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
    backdrop-filter: blur(0px);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) allow-discrete;
  }
  dialog[open]::backdrop {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  @starting-style {
    dialog[open]::backdrop {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
      backdrop-filter: blur(0px);
    }
  }
</style>
